# üñ•Ô∏è How to Add Installed Programs to the Desktop (Linux)
### Debian / Ubuntu / XFCE Guide

This guide explains **how to place installed applications on the Linux desktop**  
by creating desktop shortcuts using `.desktop` files.

---

## üîë Key Concept (Important)
Linux desktop icons are **`.desktop` launcher files**, not the actual executable.

Most application launchers are stored in:
/usr/share/applications/

yaml
Copy code

