5Ô∏è‚É£ Step 5: Allow Launching in XFCE
Right-click the desktop icon

Select ‚ÄúAllow Launching‚Äù or ‚ÄúTrust and Launch‚Äù

‚úÖ The application can now be launched by double-clicking.

6Ô∏è‚É£ Copy Multiple Applications at Once
bash
Copy code
